            "This artwork was created using drypoint, a technique that Morisot admired for its ability to produce soft, painterly effects.",
            "Morisot was one of the original members of the Impressionist group and participated in their first exhibition in 1874.",
            "Despite the challenges of being a female artist at the time, Morisot achieved significant recognition and was highly respected by her male contemporaries."
